OL,3,CHorse takes three months to recover
OL,4,Cafter being splashed by driver
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Sally Simmons has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to horse rider Esther
OL,8,Fabout the impact of fast driving on
OL,9,Fher horse Bels
OL,11,FHorse riders are warning that people
OL,12,Fare still driving too fast causing
OL,13,Funnecessary distress and harm to their
OL,14,Fanimals.
OL,16,FThe British Horse Society says road
OL,17,Fincidents in the South rose 20% last
OL,18,Fyear despite new rules being
OL,19,Fintroduced in the Highway Code.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
