PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776665107
OL,3,CHorse takes three months to recover
OL,4,Cafter being splashed by driver
OL,6,FThe changes, brought in four years
OL,7,Fago, mean drivers should pass horses
OL,8,Fat 10 miles an hour and at a two metre
OL,9,Fdistance.
OL,11,FLatest data shows eight in ten
OL,12,Fincidents were recorded of people
OL,13,Fpassing too fast or two close whilst
OL,14,Ftwo in ten involved road rage
OL,15,Fincidents.
OL,17,FIn Buckinghamshire - cases of injury
OL,18,Fjumped from 54 in 2024 to 190 last
OL,19,Fyear and in Hampshire the number of
OL,20,Fhorse deaths on roads has gone up from
OL,21,F26 in 2024 to 36 last year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
