OL,3,CHorse takes three months to recover
OL,4,Cafter being splashed by driver
OL,6,FEsther Gracereed was riding Bels on a
OL,7,Frainy wet day when a passing car drove
OL,8,Fthrough a puddle and splashed her,
OL,9,Fspooking the normally docile animal.
OL,11,FEsther was unhurt, but could tell her
OL,12,Fhorse was affected by the incident
OL,13,Fwhen she tried to get back on to get
OL,14,Fhome. It took three months for her to
OL,15,Ffully recover.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
