PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776665107
OL,3,CHorse takes three months to recover
OL,4,Cafter being splashed by driver
OL,6,F"The spray hitting Bells, it spooked
OL,7,Fher, she span, she kicked out, as a
OL,8,Ffight or flight horse, she kicked out,
OL,9,Fthat clipped the mirror of the car and
OL,10,Fonce I had control I was very
OL,11,Fconcerned, what has happened to this
OL,12,Fhorse.
OL,14,F"Bels was so shaken from it she was
OL,15,Feven backing away from me, which, it
OL,16,Fkind of hurt a little bit that she
OL,17,Fwasn't coming near me but it signalled
OL,18,Fto me that she was unhappy and scared."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
