OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776665107
OL,3,CHorse takes three months to recover
OL,4,Cafter being splashed by driver
OL,6,FIn January Newbury MP Lee Dillon
OL,7,Fcalled for a toughening of the Highway
OL,8,FCode asking that it reads "drivers
OL,9,FMUST stick to 10 mph" rather than they
OL,10,Fshould.
OL,12,FAlan Hiscox from the British Horse
OL,13,FSociety said, "78% of incidents
OL,14,Frecorded with us are because vehicles
OL,15,Fare passing too fast or too close.
OL,17,F"22% are because there's been road
OL,18,Frage incidents, and it's vehicles
OL,19,Fovertaking, but approaching from the
OL,20,Ffront as well.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776665107
OL,3,CHorse takes three months to recover
OL,4,Cafter being splashed by driver
OL,6,F"Riders are facing vehicles that are
OL,7,Fpassing too fast and too close almost
OL,8,Fdaily."
OL,10,FEsther added, "Considering these guys
OL,11,Fare all competition horses they need
OL,12,Fto go out to big events, you've got
OL,13,Ftannoys, crowds, everything like that,
OL,14,Fso the road really prepares them from
OL,15,Fthe start of their career to the end
OL,16,Fof their career, it gives them such an
OL,17,Fexperience to learn from.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776665107
OL,3,CHorse takes three months to recover
OL,4,Cafter being splashed by driver
OL,6,F"If something bad would happen, an
OL,7,Finjury etc, you do really take it to
OL,8,Fheart, because as much as we take care
OL,9,Fof them, they take care of us as well."
OL,11,FThe British Horse Society says 59
OL,12,Fhorses were killed last year and until
OL,13,Fthe number of horses and riders killed
OL,14,Fis zero, they'll continue their
OL,15,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
